_:N92361c723f154e3daac5f32968d6772f <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We cannot answer calls from individuals about benefit or pension claims. Please <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contact-jobcentre-plus\" class=\"govuk-link\">contact Jobcentre Plus</a> or <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contact-pension-service\" class=\"govuk-link\">contact The Pension Service</a> instead.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"national-and-local-media-enquiries-including-scotland-and-wales\">National and local media enquiries, including Scotland and Wales</h2>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>DWP Press Office</strong><br>\nCaxton House<br>\nTothill Street<br>\nLondon<br>\nSW1H 9NA<br>\nE-mail: <a href=\"mailto:newsdesk@dwp.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\">newsdesk@dwp.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Follow us on X <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://x.com/dwpgovuk\" class=\"govuk-link\">https://x.com/dwpgovuk</a></p>\n</div>" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
